# Auto deploy

After completing user-requested product changes, **commit and push to `origin` immediately**. Do not ask for confirmation to commit or push.

- Prefer a concise commit message focused on why.
- Never commit secrets (`.env`, `env.yaml`, credentials, private keys).
- Do not use `--force` on main/master unless the user explicitly demands it.
- After push, briefly confirm that it is on the remote / deploying.
